{
  "id": "adv_card_chs_03_02",
  "title": "白石千紗",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "1、2、3、4……1、2、3、4……",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……やる気は伝わってくるが……\nやはり急なパート変更ですぐにうまくはいかないか",
      "startTime": 11.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "1、2、3、4……きゃっ！",
      "startTime": 15.5333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4100.000000000002,
          "startTime": 19.6333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫か！？\n今日は朝から踊りっぱなしだろ、少し休憩した方がいい",
      "startTime": 22.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁはぁ……でも、ライブまで時間がありませんから\n早く踊れるようにならないと……",
      "startTime": 32.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "気持ちは分かるが無理はするな\nなんならコーチにお願いして難易度を下げても……",
      "startTime": 38.3433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "難易度は下げたくありません\nお願いします、このままの振り付けでやらせて下さい",
      "startTime": 44.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "週末までにはきっと……\nいえ、必ず、踊れるようになってみせますから",
      "startTime": 51.3433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……分かった\nだが無理は禁物だ。いいな？",
      "startTime": 58.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――千紗、別件の仕事中",
      "startTime": 63.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 63.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 63.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "1、2、3、4……ここでターンして……",
      "startTime": 65.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "千紗、もうすぐグラビアの撮影が始まるけど……\n何を観てるんだ？",
      "startTime": 76.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 79.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "自分のダンスを撮影した動画です\nどうしてもうまく踊れないところがあって……",
      "startTime": 82.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "動画で動きを確認してるんですけど\n観れば観るほど自分の下手さが目についちゃって……",
      "startTime": 89,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 94.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "こんなことじゃダメですよね……\nもっと努力しないと……",
      "startTime": 97.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 99.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "仕事の合間にイメージトレーニングか……\n千紗もいろいろと工夫してるんだな",
      "startTime": 103.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（この頑張りに応えてやりたいが）\n（俺に何か出来ることは……）",
      "startTime": 109.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 112.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 112.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "はぁはぁ……\nダメ……どうしても同じところでミスしちゃう……",
      "startTime": 117.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……千紗。ここ数日レッスンを見てきたが\nこのまま同じことをしていても上達は難しいと思う",
      "startTime": 125.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "酷なことを言うようだが、間に合わせるにはやはり\n振り付けの難易度を下げるしかないんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 132.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "それは……嫌です\nお願いします、このままやらせて下さい",
      "startTime": 139.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてそこまで頑ななんだ？　難易度を下げても\nこれだけ頑張った千紗を誰も責めたりしないさ",
      "startTime": 146.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね……\nみんな優しいから私を責めないと思います……",
      "startTime": 152.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私が嫌なんです……諦めたくないんです",
      "startTime": 156.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "私が怜ちゃんのかわりに踊るって決めた後\n寮に戻ってサニピのみんなと話したんです",
      "startTime": 165.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "ソロパートをやりたいって言い出したのは私だから\n私の口からちゃんと説明しなきゃと思って……",
      "startTime": 173.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs016.m4a",
      "text": "星見市にいた頃は目の前のことで精一杯だったけど\n東京に出て、いろんなお仕事をするようになって……",
      "startTime": 183.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs017.m4a",
      "text": "少しだけ視野が広がって……私が頑張れば\nもっといろんな景色が見られるんだって分かって……",
      "startTime": 192.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs018.m4a",
      "text": "もっと挑戦したい……もっと成長したい……\nそう思えるようになったから……",
      "startTime": 200.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs019.m4a",
      "text": "だから、今度のソロパートは私に挑戦させてほしいって\nみんなにお願いしたんです",
      "startTime": 208.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "内気な千紗が自分から挑戦したいと言い出すなんて\nみんな驚いたんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 214.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs020.m4a",
      "text": "はい……でも、みんなすぐに賛成してくれました\nそうしようって言ってくれて……",
      "startTime": 221.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs021.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃんは、ひたむきに努力してきた\n千紗ちゃんなら絶対出来るよって言ってくれて……",
      "startTime": 227.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs022.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃんは、私がソロパートを\nかっこよく踊る姿を見たいって言ってくれて……",
      "startTime": 235.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs023.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんは、私達がサポートするから\n安心して踊っていいんだよって……",
      "startTime": 243.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs024.m4a",
      "text": "それに怜ちゃんは……「最近の千紗が熱心にダンスに\n取り組んでいたのを、ずっとそばで見てたから……」",
      "startTime": 250.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
